| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2247 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 18d51d6f-ebcb-52d6-a86c-a6de6479e767"
